# ✅ REWARDS PORTAL — SETUP GUIDE
# Yeh sab steps ek baar karo — phir sab kaam karega

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🔵 STEP 1 — DISCORD OAUTH FIX

1. Jao: https://discord.com/developers/applications
2. Apni app select karo (Client ID: 1352652069359587430)
3. Left sidebar → "OAuth2" click karo
4. "Redirects" section mein:
   - PURANA hatao:  https://www.elevateiq.shop/index.html   ❌
   - NAYA daalo:    https://www.elevateiq.shop/              ✅
5. "Save Changes" karo

Bas! Discord ab theek kaam karega.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🟦 STEP 2 — AZURE / MICROSOFT AUTH FIX

Error tha: "unauthorized_client — not enabled for consumers"
Matlab app sirf Work/School accounts ke liye thi. Personal accounts ke liye yeh karo:

1. Jao: https://portal.azure.com
2. Left menu → "Azure Active Directory" (ya "Microsoft Entra ID")
3. "App registrations" → Apni app select karo
4. Left sidebar → "Authentication" click karo

5. "Supported account types" mein SELECT KARO:
   ✅ "Accounts in any organizational directory (Any Microsoft Entra ID tenant – Multitenant)
       AND personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. Skype, Xbox)"
   (Teen options mein se TEESRA wala)

6. "Redirect URIs" mein check karo:
   - Type: "Single-page application (SPA)"   ← ZAROOR SPA select karo
   - URI:  https://www.elevateiq.shop/        ✅

7. "Save" karo

8. Left sidebar → "Overview" → "Application (client) ID" copy karo
   Yeh ID shared.js mein daalni hai (Step 4 dekho)

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🟩 STEP 3 — VERCEL CLEAN URLs

vercel.json file already folder mein hai.
Bas deploy karo — URLs automatically clean ho jayenge:
  ❌ elevateiq.shop/redeem.html
  ✅ elevateiq.shop/redeem

Agar subfolder mein deploy kar rahe ho (e.g. /eiq/):
  vercel.json ke rewrites mein /eiq/ prefix add karo.
  Recommend hai ROOT mein deploy karo.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🟪 STEP 4 — shared.js mein CLIENT ID DAALO

shared.js file kholo, line 12 find karo:

  AZURE_CLIENT: 'YOUR_AZURE_CLIENT_ID_HERE'

Isko apni actual Azure Client ID se replace karo:

  AZURE_CLIENT: 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🚀 STEP 5 — VERCEL DEPLOY

Option A — Drag & Drop:
  1. vercel.com/new
  2. Saari files drag karo (index.html, shared.js, shared.css, etc.)
  3. Deploy karo

Option B — GitHub se:
  1. GitHub pe repo banao
  2. Saari files push karo
  3. vercel.com → "Import Git Repository"
  4. Root directory: / (jahan index.html hai)
  5. Deploy

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ✅ CHECKLIST — Deploy se pehle

[ ] Discord OAuth2 redirect URL updated to https://www.elevateiq.shop/
[ ] Azure app → Supported accounts → "Personal + Organizational" selected
[ ] Azure app → Authentication → Redirect URI type = SPA
[ ] Azure Client ID shared.js mein daala
[ ] vercel.json folder mein hai
[ ] Sabhi .html files ek hi folder mein hain

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ❓ COMMON ERRORS

Q: Discord login ke baad blank page
A: Discord Developer Portal mein redirect URL check karo — exactly https://www.elevateiq.shop/ honi chahiye (trailing slash ke saath)

Q: Microsoft login mein "unauthorized_client" error
A: Azure app mein "Supported account types" galat hai — Step 2 dobara karo

Q: Microsoft login mein "redirect_uri_mismatch"
A: Azure app → Authentication → SPA redirect URI = https://www.elevateiq.shop/ (exactly same)

Q: Coins page change pe reset ho jaate hain
A: Sab localStorage mein hain — agar incognito mode mein ho toh yahi hoga. Normal mode mein persist rahega.
